## Network manager
bindsym $mod+KP_Add exec nmcli c up Ac
bindsym $mod+KP_Subtract exec nmcli c down Ac
bindsym $mod+Shift+KP_Add exec nmcli c up `nmcli c show Ac | grep "connection.secondaries:" | awk '{ print $2 }'`
bindsym $mod+Shift+KP_Subtract exec nmcli c down `nmcli c show Ac | grep "connection.secondaries:" | awk '{ print $2 }'`

## Screenshot
bindsym Print exec --no-startup-id flameshot screen -p ~/Pictures/screenshots -c
bindsym $mod+Print exec --no-startup-id flameshot gui

## Picom shortcut
bindsym $mod+Shift+p exec --no-startup-id picom-refresh

## Gaps shortcuts
bindsym $mod+plus  gaps inner all plus 2
bindsym $mod+minus  gaps inner all minus 2
bindsym $mod+Shift+plus  gaps outer all plus 2
bindsym $mod+Shift+minus  gaps outer all minus 2
bindsym $mod+bracketleft  gaps vertical all plus 2
bindsym $mod+bracketright  gaps vertical all minus 2
bindsym $mod+Shift+bracketleft  gaps horizontal all plus 2
bindsym $mod+Shift+bracketright  gaps horizontal all minus 2
